Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中出現了一道巨大的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都以七色來稱呼彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管語言文化都各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是身為世界意志的偉大存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是諸神的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在諸神守望地上時出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(小小女孩 開始嶄新的生活)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽一臉鬱悶的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一段時間驅除魔獸的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿到拉提娜那時的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要向委託人做工作完成的報告才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都是切下魔獸身體的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當作證明帶過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些東西很臭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢帶進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要禁止你進出了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要帶著委託人去那裡做確認才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不能帶著拉提娜過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓她留在店裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起讓你一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法拋下拉提娜自己去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拋下委託人不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定會死守住拉提娜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙好像沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇拉提娜或許也是一種選項啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你晚上就能回來 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要出遠門的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也差不多快來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就這副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打從一開始說要照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是天方夜譚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(我 不在)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(拉提娜 等)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(這裡)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是惹人憐愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡量早點回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要乖乖地做個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你也差不多該走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說路上小心 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 路上咬心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很快就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點 肯尼斯　　來 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天一早還有護衛任務要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照順序來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撲滅搗亂田地的魔獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只剩些吃力不討好的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 找你的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想找合乎需求的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能頻繁做確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古達爾的傳言板的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是即刻做更新的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 拿酒來 拿酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必那麼大聲 我也聽得見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們僱用了一個小小的服務生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是白費工夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚那女人一定對我有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你努力的獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肯尼斯做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉塔 我要出門補貨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子果然很厲害啊 莉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生三個 你覺得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生出第一個再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一下子就變成大紅人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 你回來得真…　　拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 我回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連歡迎回來都學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會看家了 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你交了個這麼小的女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你整張臉都鬆弛下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜有做個乖孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她簡直是乖巧過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的頭腦真的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在店頭幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很清楚所處的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有自己應該要做甚麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那個薯蓉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是拉提娜幫忙做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉提娜做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一盤 再來一盤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的薯蓉我要全部吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊就是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才過了一個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經變得很會說話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我每天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會用繪本教她說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是…好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小孩子成長得真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 她算是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但融會貫通的速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也懂得體諒他人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀明明就還那麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來簡直就像一對父女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個肯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然這麼會攏絡小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有一點笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但教她東西很快就會學會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連肯尼斯都覺得很佩服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手滑掉了 危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然她自己想做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要尊重她的意願才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你這麼在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆不要看就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就會錯過拉提娜的成長了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去一趟東區
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘記薯仔快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薯仔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有薯仔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法做薯蓉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能做薯蓉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起 拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她這樣盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪可能有辦法說不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那樣未免太幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然有肯尼斯在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗語也都說要讓孩子出門見識…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是有所成長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以離開肯尼斯身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 會跟肯尼斯在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟迪爾出門買衣服後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒再逛街了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓貓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說拉提娜迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為她有一直跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然她都已經迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今不管再說甚麼也都無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這種事也沒辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該要先學搜索系魔法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不需要學的過去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我向拉提娜道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如先去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守門的衛兵是店裡的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有哪個笨蛋想把她帶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到城牆那邊就會被攔下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也會自己想辦法才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要願意一起幫忙找人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的酒錢就算免費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找走失的小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺比對付幻獸還棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾維斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裡的看板娘行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好喝的酒也喝不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會再付一份酬謝金的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算找不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在賽基之刻回來就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打發一下時間也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣那傢伙人情也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪家的小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒看過這種髮色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貴族的小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是貴族的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會穿禮服的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少見的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不像金色 也不像銀色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是外地來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為甚麼要生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子都快哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是問問她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪邊的小孩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為甚麼要逃跑啊 很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是外國的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然欺負這麼小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手啊 克蘿伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣 你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢欺負弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對放過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然還會是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種愛動口又動手的壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點改一改啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎 不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要塗點口水就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蘿伊每次都這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法說話 拉提娜不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對的人是嚇到你的我們才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天之光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名實現祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請治癒負傷之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癒光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔法師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼小竟然會使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裡幾乎沒有人會使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神殿或領主大人身邊工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是大商會的人會用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是冒險者了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒險者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜 店裡 回去 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是她迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說店裡 你是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎貓的店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎貓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南區掛有綠旗的那間店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得就是叫這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒險者的店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒險者 好多來到店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉提娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還會用其他甚麼魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟剛才不一樣的 你會用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有治療魔法而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只會一種也很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽有交代過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子不要自己跑到南區
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說甚麼啊 安東尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在可是在幫助人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說那裡有很多外人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或危險分子的傳言…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我們是要帶這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你很久了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 他們要送你回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他們認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就先…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要送她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽不負責到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送這孩子回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼斯 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你們帶拉提娜回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助朋友是理所當然的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們和拉提娜成為朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再陪拉提娜慢慢玩吧
